msgid ""
"Add ``MM_`` to the beginning and convert all characters to uppercase and "
"replace the ``.`` with ``_``. For example, *MM_SERVICESETTINGS_SITEURL*."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/administration/prev-config-settings.rst:21
msgid ""
"The setting becomes ``export "
"MM_SERVICESETTINGS_SITEURL=\"http://example.com\"``."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/administration/prev-config-settings.rst:23
msgid ""
"Finally, if a setting is configured through an environment variable, "
"modifying it in the System Console is disabled."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/administration/prev-config-settings.rst:25
msgid ""
"For any setting that is not set in ``config.json`` or in environment "
"variables, the Mattermost server uses the default value as documented "
"here."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/administration/prev-config-settings.rst:28
msgid ""
